Type: Package
Package: modelsummary
Title: Summary Tables for Statistical Models: Beautiful, Customizable, and
    Publication-Ready 
Description: Create beautiful and customizable summary tables for statistical
    models. 'modelsummary' leverages the power of the 'gt', 'kableExtra' and
    'broom' packages. It can produce tables in HTML, LaTeX, RTF, Text/Markdown,
    JPG, PNG, and LaTeX formats. The tables can be integrated in Rmarkdown,
    knitr, or Sweave dynamic documents.
Version: 0.3.0
